data.description: Experience the comfort of main level living in this charming townhome nestled in Northridge/Eagleridge.   The 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout comes with an attached garage. The inviting entrance leads to an open-plan living, dining, and kitchen area. The living room is enhanced by well-maintained wood laminate flooring and an abundance of natural light from the plentiful windows. A superb kitchen features a breakfast bar, pine cabinets, stainless-steel appliances, and a writing desk space.   Beyond the kitchen, discover a guest bedroom with carpeted flooring and a walk-in closet. A spacious hall closet provides additional storage. The primary bedroom is a retreat with an en-suite bathroom, walk-in closet, and sliding door access to the fenced backyard.   The backyard offers beautiful landscaping, a well-kept wood deck, and a gate for easy front and back yard access.   The HOA covers lawn and exterior maintenance, snow and trash removal, structure insurance, and both interior and exterior water.
